title: Democratic Debate Recap & Key Takeaways
itunes:title: Democratic Debate Recap & Key Takeaways
description:
Kevin spoke with Max Burns, Democratic Strategist; Senior Contributor at Millennial Politics, Hagar Chemali, CEO of Greenwich Media Strategies and former Treasury spokesperson for Terrorism and Financial Intelligence, and Julie Roginsky, Democratic Strategist.

They discussed the biggest takeaways from the October Democratic debate.
